<br>
The rain one only &quot;appears&quot; to make you stand (thus why the sit/stand button doesn't change) each time a wave lands which is an annoying graphical bug but won't stop you meditating.  Affectionately referred to as &quot;Rain Dancing&quot;.<br>
<br>
The fact that subsequent waves of the rain require you to maintain LOS to the mob the rain is landing on is stupid, and one of the major reasons I only ever use DD's rather than rains against AE mobs (as you can't hide around the corner after you have cast the rain).<br>
<br>
Summon Companion when you're levitating in an area the pet can't path to will make the pet despawn - handy as you've fallen into a trap while levitate is up and you're slowly descending into 3 mobs...<br>
<br>
Your pet stops moving towards you if you get too close to a wall.  Should just path to the last 'pathing point' you were next to.<br>
<br>
CotH a pet class and it destroys their pet.  Should bring the pet with them.<br>
<br>
